<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2013/01/android-developer-story-smule.html'>Android Developer Story: Smule</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7572844686291126520' itemprop='articlesBody'>
<p>Check out our latest Android developer story, this one from Smule, creators of <a href="//play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smule.autorap">AutoRap</a>, <a href="//play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smule.magicpiano">Magic Piano</a>, and <a href="//play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.smule.songify">Songify</a>. 
</p>

<p>In this short video, the Smule team talks about their experiences launching on Android, the explosive global growth they&#8217;ve seen on Google Play, and some of the techniques they use to market and monetize their products effectively across the world.</p>
<br />
<iframe width="700" height="394" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/RRelFvc6Czo" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
